chirptask.storage

Interface IStorage

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventLogger, GoogleStorage, LocalStorage, SessionStorage

    public interface IStorage
    Storage interface provides default methods for storage type classes. Methods: storeNewTask, removeTask, modifyTask, getTask, getAllTasks, close.
